									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">标签有</span> <a href="http://www.oldcai.com/?tag=wordpress" rel="tag">wordpress</a>、<a href="http://www.oldcai.com/?tag=%e5%8f%8b%e6%83%85%e9%93%be%e6%8e%a5" rel="tag">友情链接</a>、<a href="http://www.oldcai.com/?tag=%e6%98%be%e7%a4%ba" rel="tag">显示</a>、<a href="http://www.oldcai.com/?tag=%e9%a6%96%e9%a1%b5" rel="tag">首页</a>			</span>
						
